# Task Intake

Pre-triage capture. Raw notes, observations, and rough ideas that may or
may not become tasks. No id, no file, no commitment beyond "I wrote it
down" — the lowest-friction layer in the lifecycle. When an entry
matures, promote it to triage via `/task promote` (creates a `TASK-NNN`
stub in `tasks/triage/`) — or drop it.

